text: Fu Yu (; born November 29, 1978) is a Chinese-born Portuguese table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's singles event, in which she was eliminated in the second round by Nanthana Komwong. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese emigrants to Portugal Category:Portuguese female table tennis players Category:Chinese female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Portugal Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players from Hebei Category:Naturalised table tennis players Category:European Games medalists in table tennis Category:Table tennis players at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Portugal Category:European Games gold medalists for Portugal
